      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Finely chop your <strong>toasted walnuts</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1674576516763-x200.jpg",
