            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once tender, add the <strong>drained linguine </strong>to the pan with a splash of the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the pasta is fully coated – this is your <strong>mushroom & asparagus linguine</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
