            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mushroom & asparagus linguine </strong>with the <strong>salad</strong> to the side and season with a good grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add a small squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> over the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted walnuts</strong> and a <strong>remaining lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
